bilingual.source: A failed cwr can cause data loss.
bilingual.target: 失败的计算机写入请求可能导致数据丢失。

bilingual.source: She mockingly laughed at his failed attempt.
bilingual.target: 她嘲讽地嘲笑了他失败的尝试。

bilingual.source: The failed policy was unlamented by the citizens.
bilingual.target: 失败的政策没有受到市民的哀悼。

bilingual.source: She gave him a mocky smile after his failed attempt.
bilingual.target: 在他失败的尝试后，她给了他一个嘲讽的微笑。

bilingual.source: The main reason we failed is the lack of experience.
bilingual.target: 我们失败的主要原因是缺乏经验。

bilingual.source: The company squandered its resources on a failed project.
bilingual.target: 公司把资源浪费在一个失败的项目上。

bilingual.source: He regretted the wasted resources on the failed experiment.
bilingual.target: 他后悔在失败的实验上浪费了资源。

bilingual.source: The book tells the story of a failed assassination attempt.
bilingual.target: 这本书讲述了一次失败的暗杀行动。

bilingual.source: Her frustration was evident when she spoke about her failed project.
bilingual.target: 当她谈到她失败的项目时，她的沮丧显而易见。

bilingual.source: If you don't learn something when you fail, then all you've done is failed.
bilingual.target: 如果你失败的时候不吸取教训，那么你所做的一切都是失败的。

list.abstract: failed（英 [feɪld]，美 [feɪld]），英语单词。原形：fail。作形容词为未达目的的；不持久的；失败的等。例句：The French measures have already failed.（法国的措施已经失败。） failed的近义词有unsuccessful，unfortunate，defeated。反义词有succeed，manage，pass。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't wanna hear three failed marriages. Look, if you'd had two failed marriages, you'd understand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想听三次失败的婚姻。如果你失败过两次就会了解了。

yingyinNormal.en: He's never trusted us. He already thinks we're behind Milkin's failed coup.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他从未信任过我们，他已经觉得我们操纵了米尔金失败的政变。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, well, being a failed scientist doesn't pay quite as well as you might think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，一个失败的科学家，并没有你想像的赚的多。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not kidding. Look, I can't have three failed marriages. I can't. Okay? I am not gonna be that guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是啊，我不能有三次失败的婚姻，我不能，好吗？我不要当那个人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm gonna need more. Okay, failed actress who traded constant rejection for a Christmas bonus and a dental plan?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样不够。失败的女演员为了不一直被拒绝出卖灵魂好得到年终奖金与牙科医保？

yingyinNormal.en: And you are going to hear from witness after witness who will tell you that Chad, a failed entrepreneur, couldn't handle his wife's success, that their marriage was on the rocks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而你们将会听到一个又一个证人向你们描述查德，一个失败的企业家，无法接受他妻子的成功，他们的婚姻岌岌可危。

yingyinNormal.en: Congress failed him. Congress failed you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 国会让他失望了。国会让人民失望了。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, Ms. Hart? you failed me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请说，哈特小姐。你给我打了不及格。

yingyinNormal.en: I counted on you. That's why you failed. What?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我那么信任你。所以你失败了。什么？

yingyinNormal.en: I never meant for this to happen. I failed them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从来没想过会发生这种事，我让他们失望了。

yingyinNormal.en: So that's it, then? We failed? We're done. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 言下之意 我们失败了? 抱歉，我们失败了。

yingyinNormal.en: So, because you failed once, you're just running away?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，因为你失败过一次，你就要逃跑了？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, Plankton, I guess we failed to accomplish our goals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，痞老板，我想我们是失败了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: Lockhart/Gardner. And, in fact, wasn't it Lockhart/Gardner who failed you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 洛&加律所。事实上，不正是他们搞砸了领养。

yingyinNormal.en: You have failed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你失败了。

yingyinNormal.en: How do you know the theory of evolution? Because I failed it. I know it because I failed it, but he made sure I knew it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是怎么知道进化论的？因为我之前没答上来。我之前没答对，所以我记住了，但是他确保了我记住。

yingyinNormal.en: That was a test, and you just failed. Damn it! Rookie mistake!
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是个测试，你没过关。该死的！新手失误！

yingyinNormal.en: Second one I failed, thanks to you. And the car bomb was insurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多亏你，我没能杀了第二个人。而汽车炸弹则是最后的杀手锏。

yingyinNormal.en: You failed. And do you wanna know why? Because you love nothing. No one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你失败了。知道为什么吗？因为你没有爱过。你谁也不爱。

yingyinNormal.en: When you two programmed him to protect the human race, you amazingly failed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你们俩把他编程为保护人类时，你们的失败真让人惊讶。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Years of experience in the industry - and <highlight>failed</highlight> attempts to use technology - have convinced him.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多年的行业经验，以及使用技术的失败尝试，让他信服了。
